                     <interp inst="t17920912-77-person716" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I apprehended the prisoner (corresponds with the last witness.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920912-77-person717">
                  JOSEPH
                   FISHER
               <interp inst="t17920912-77-person717" type="surname" value="FISHER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920912-77-person717" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920912-77-person717" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have been two or three times with the prisoner at this house; I know it was his house.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920912-77-person718">
                  JOSEPH
                   MIFLIN
               <interp inst="t17920912-77-person718" type="surname" value="MIFLIN"></interp>
